snippet.title: The GOAT (Official Trailer) Tamil: Thalapathy Vijay | Venkat Prabhu | Yuvan Shankar Raja | T-Series
snippet.description:

snippet.title: Rakesh Barot | રાકેશ બારોટ | Reshma Thakor | રેશ્મા ઠાકોર | સોના રૂપનિ ભમ્મર વેલ | ગુજરાતી ગીત 2024
snippet.description:
સાંભળો રાકેશ બારોટ અને રેશ્મા ઠાકોરનું નવું  ગીત સોના રૂપાણી ભમ્મર વહેલ ફક્ત @SaregamaGujarati પર

Listen to Rakesh Barot and Reshma Thakor's new happy song "Sona Roopani Bhammar Vehl" only on @SaregamaGujarati 

Credits:
Singer: Rakesh Barot, Reshma Thakor 
Producer: Red Velvet Cinema 
Artist: Rakesh Barot, Sweat  sen , Divya Rajani ,kirtiy kashiya 
Concept: Savya Bhati , Bhavesh Gorsiya
Director: Bhavesh Gorasiya
Creative Head: Dhyey Films & Team
Technical Support: Jenish Talaviya
Production Manager: Ramesh Halol 
Lyrics: Chandu Raval
Music: Rakesh Barot, Mehul Barot
Dop: Anu Patel ( viral )
choreographer Dipak turi 
Editor: Anu Patel ( viral )
Makeup & Hair : chirag parmar, mandakini                            
Rakesh Barot Costume: Manisha R Barot
Recoding: Dhoon Digital Recoding Studio Adalaj
lokeshan Richiya gaam ( Halol )

Lyrics:
હે હાવ હોના ની હે એવી રૂપા ની
હે હાવ હોના રે રૂપા ની ભમ્મર વેલ
વેલડીએ ઘમકે છે જેણી ગુગર માણા રાજ
હે જોડો પરણિયા જોડો ભમ્મર વેલ
કોનુંડો આયો ને મૈયર જાવું માણા રાજ
હે ચાર પાંચ દાડા થી મને એ બધી ખબર છે
તારા રે પિયર સોમે તારી રે નજર છે
હે લોમી લોમી છે હે ઘણી છેટી
હે લોમી લોમી છે તારા મૈયરયા ની વાટ
ઘૂઘરા રે ધમકાવી વેલડું છોડું માણા રાજ
હે કોનુંડો આયો ને મૈયર જાવું માણા રાજ
હે વ્હલી મારી મૈયર જઇ ને તમે મોરે થઇ રમજો
મોરે થઈને રમશો તો અમને બહુ ગમશો
ઓ ભવો ભવ ભરથાર થઇ ને મળજો
તમારા પહેલા પિયુ મોત મને આવજો
ઓ પિયુ તમે બોલો વાત મા તહેવારે
નથી રોકી જતી પિયર જાત મને તહેવારે
હે હું ચંપો ને (૩) તમે છો મારી કેળ
કોનુંડો રમી ને રાજી રેજો મારા રાજ
કોનુંડો આયો ને મૈયર જાવું માણા  રાજ
હો આયો કોનુંડો પિયુ હૈયે હરખ છે હેંડો અવે મોડું રે થાય છે
હો તારું પિયર ને ગોડી મારું છે સાસરું
ચિંતા ના કરો વેલડું જશે રે પોચડું
હે મારી ગોથેનો ભેગી રે થઇ છે વટિયો મારી જોઈ બેઠી છે
હે ઉગિયો ઉગિયો રે (2)
હે ઉગિયો ઉગિયો રે, સોમે પિયેરે પ્રારભત
દાડો આથમતા પહોંચી જાસુ રે મારા રાજ
હે આવે કોનુંડો રમી રાજી થશુ મારા રાજ
હે આવે કોનુંડો રમી રાજી રેજો મારા રાજ

snippet.title: Brother Vs Sister Roblox Challenge
snippet.description:
Today I challenge my sister in Roblox. #Roblox is a fun free game! 

This game is also available on Android and its free to download! My sister plays this game on her Android Tab everyday and she thinks she can defeat me in a Roblox battle
I am an Android Lover 😎 and I have played lot of Android Games so I am Pro at this and I will definitely win this match! Gaming is smooth on Android because Game Mode Rocks 💯 Happy to be part of Team Android 😎 Suggest me some more android games to play in my next videos!

snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 4167: Paani Khatam
--------------------------------------------------------
Popatlal is furious when the water stops mid-shower. He storms down and blames Bhide for the inconvenience. How will the society members react to Popatlal's outburst?

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - Ep 4167 | 19 Aug 2024
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2024 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #15yearsoftmkoc  #4000episodes

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :
https://www.sonyliv.com/shows/taarak-mehta-ka-ooltah-chashmah-1000286847

Kaffara Episode 23 - [Eng Sub] - Ali Ansari - Laiba Khan - Zoya Nasir - 19th August 2024 - HAR PAL GEO

Sitara, a lively orphan living with her brother, aunt, and uncle, finds joy in life's small things despite her aunt's poor treatment. Her aunt keeps her around because she has a share in the family's property.
Salar, the son of a wealthy businessman, is passionate about photography, which often earns him criticism from his family. With a pure heart, Salar is known for evading his responsibilities.
At her cousin's wedding, Sitara wrongly assumes Salar is the photographer. Salar develops a soft spot for Sitara after seeing how poorly she is treated. However, due to a conspiracy, objections arise about their closeness. Salar, once again, avoids the issue, leaving Sitara to face doubts from her own family.
Can Sitara prove she’s not guilty? Will Salar help her avoid further mistreatment? Will her family support Sitara? Can Salar show he genuinely cares? Will there be more plots against Sitara?

snippet.title: Adharinchumayya | ఆదరించుమయ్యా | Suhaas Prince | CalvaryTemple New Song 2024 #drsatishkumar
snippet.description:
CREDITS:
Lyrics : Dr.P.Satish Kumar Garu 
Tune : Bro. Suhaas Prince & Bro. Sunnel
Music : Bro. V. Sandeep Kumar
Vocals : Bro. Suhaas Prince

                   SONG LYRICS
॥పల్లవి||
ఆదరించుమయ్యా  ఆదుకొనేవాడా 
చేరదీయుమయ్యా  సేదదీర్చేవాడా
యేసయ్య  యేసయ్య  నీ మీదే నా ఆశయ్య

చరణం:
రెక్కలే విరిగినా  గువ్వనై నే వొరిగినా
ఎండలో వాడినా  పువ్వునై నే రాలినా 
దిక్కు తోచక నిన్ను చేరితి
కాదనవని నిన్ను నే వేడితి
నను దర్శించుమో యేసయ్య  ||2||
నను ధైర్యపరచుమో నా యేసయ్యా 

చరణం:
ఆశలే అడుగంటెనే  నిరాశలే ఆవరించనే  
నీడయే కరువాయెనే  నా గూడుయే చెదరిపోయెనే
నీ తోడు నే కోరుకొంటిని
నీ పిలుపుకై వేచియుంటిని
నీ దరిచేర్చుకో- యేసయ్య  ||2|| 
నన్ను కాదనకుమా నా యేసయ్యా

His teachings, which are both powerful and simple, have had a profound impact on the lives of countless individuals, leading them to transform from wickedness to Godliness. His acceptance and respect among people from all regions and religions stem from his refusal to complain, condemn, criticize, or compare other Gods or religions. Instead, his teachings focus on convicting individuals of their wicked ways, rather than simply converting them.

As an Indian, Dr. Satish Kumar proudly represents his country on international platforms, speaking highly of Indian values, culture, and the importance of family structure. He strongly emphasizes the belief that "Service to mankind is service to God," echoing the words of Jesus who said, "Love your neighbor as you love yourself." Dr. Satish Kumar not only preaches this philosophy, but also practices it in his own life.

Dr. SatishKumar, a renowned spiritual leader, delivers impactful sermons that have the power to transform lives and guide individuals towards a blessed and prosperous spiritual journey. His teachings cover a wide range of life-related topics such as acceptance, brokenness, calling, comfort, crisis, decisions, doubt, endurance, giving, healing, hurts, loss, love, miracles, mistakes, planning, purpose, risk, stress, temptation, tragedy, and wisdom, among others.

snippet.title: B Praak - Mukke Paye Si | Sunny Kaushal | Neha Sharma | Sagar | Bunny | Arvvindr S Khaira
snippet.description:
B Praak returns to Desi Melodies with the soul-stirring, "Mukke Paaye Si." It is a story featuring Sunny Kaushal and Neha Sharma of lost love along with the lingering pain it leaves behind, resonating with anyone who has felt the ache of a broken heart and reminding us of the strength required to endure a heartbreak. 

Listen to 'Mukke Paye Si' on your favourite streaming platform - https://umgindia.lnk.to/MPS

snippet.title: Mahindra Thar Roxx 2WD AX7L- ₹20.4 lakh | Real-life review
snippet.description:
Namaste friends, please LIKE & SUBSCRIBE :)

The Mahindra Thar Roxx is a five-door variant of the Thar SUV, launched by Mahindra & Mahindra in India on August 15, 2024. This model is designed to offer additional space and modern features while maintaining the off-road capabilities for which the Thar line-up is known. The Thar Roxx is built on Mahindra's new M_Glyde platform. It gets India’s First Crawl Smart Assist and IntelliTurn which can conquer tough terrains and tight turns with ease for superior off-road maneuverability. It also gets expansive Panoramic Skyroof which provides a wide open-air view, enhancing the sense of space in every drive. Also equipped with Harman Kardon 9-speaker system with QuantumLogic and Twin HD screens. #Mahindra #TharRoxx #MahindraTharRoxx

Petrol: 1997 cc, Inline-4 cylinder,  G20 mStallion engine with Turbo Petrol Direct Injection (TGDI), Automatic- 174 HP Power, 380 Nm Torque, Manual- 159 HP Power, 330 Nm Torque, Approx. 12 kmpl Average, 57 litre Fuel Tank, 6-speed Manual or 6-speed Aisin Torque Converter Automatic Transmission

Diesel: 2184 cc, Inline-4 cylinder, D22 mHawk engine with 1600 bar Common Rail Direct Injection Technology, RWD- 150 HP Power, 330 Nm Torque, 4WD- 172 HP Power, 370 Nm Torque, Approx. 15 kmpl Average, 57 litre Fuel Tank, 6-speed Manual or 6-speed Aisin Torque Converter Automatic Transmission

4 Variants: MX1, MX3, AX3L, MX5, AX5L, AX7L

2 Upholsteries: Black Fabric, Beige Leatherette

3 Wheels: 18 inch Steel, 18 inch Alloy, 19 inch Diamond Cut Alloy

7 Colours: Black, Blue, Grey, Brown, Red, White, Stealth Black

Price range (Excluding 4WD): Rs. 12.99 lakh - Rs. 20.49 lakh (Ex-showroom, Delhi)

Jaan Nisar Episode 45 - [Eng Sub] - Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints - Danish Taimoor - Hiba Bukhari - Haroon Shahid - 17th August 2024 - Har Pal Geo

Jaan Nisar Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints

7th Sky Entertainment’s mega project, Jaan Nisar, is the most awaited drama serial of the year.
The highly anticipated project marks the return of the successful on-screen couple of Danish Taimoor and Hiba Bukhari in an unforgettable love story that will steal your heart.

Nosherwan Ghaznavi, a wealthy young man, faces a pivotal moment in his life after his brother's death. This tragedy burdens Nosherwan Ghaznavi with numerous responsibilities, which he reluctantly accepts, only to find them later proving detrimental. However, his life takes a transformative turn upon meeting Dua, falling in love with her at first sight, but it places him at a critical juncture with his responsibilities.

Dua, a beautiful girl from a humble background, is raised by her parents alongside her two sisters. Despite her innocence, fate subjects Dua to a string of misfortunes before encountering Nosherwan Ghaznavi. However, their meeting completely changes their lives.

Will Nowsherwan Ghaznavi find love? What challenges will he face in balancing his duties and his love for Dua? Will his responsibilities jeopardize his love for Dua? What past events have shaped Dua's life, and will they resurface to trouble her? Will Dua return Nowsherwan Ghaznavi’s love?

7th Sky Entertainment’s mega project, Jaan Nisar, is the most awaited drama serial of the year.
The highly anticipated project marks the return of the successful on-screen couple of Danish Taimoor and Hiba Bukhari in an unforgettable love story that will steal your heart.

Nosherwan Ghaznavi, a wealthy young man, faces a pivotal moment in his life after his brother's death. This tragedy burdens Nosherwan Ghaznavi with numerous responsibilities, which he reluctantly accepts, only to find them later proving detrimental. However, his life takes a transformative turn upon meeting Dua, falling in love with her at first sight, but it places him at a critical juncture with his responsibilities.

Dua, a beautiful girl from a humble background, is raised by her parents alongside her two sisters. Despite her innocence, fate subjects Dua to a string of misfortunes before encountering Nosherwan Ghaznavi. However, their meeting completely changes their lives.

Will Nowsherwan Ghaznavi find love? What challenges will he face in balancing his duties and his love for Dua? Will his responsibilities jeopardize his love for Dua? What past events have shaped Dua's life, and will they resurface to trouble her? Will Dua return Nowsherwan Ghaznavi’s love?

snippet.description:

Kaffara Episode 22 - [Eng Sub] - Ali Ansari - Laiba Khan - Zoya Nasir - 18th August 2024 - HAR PAL GEO

Sitara, a lively orphan living with her brother, aunt, and uncle, finds joy in life's small things despite her aunt's poor treatment. Her aunt keeps her around because she has a share in the family's property.
Salar, the son of a wealthy businessman, is passionate about photography, which often earns him criticism from his family. With a pure heart, Salar is known for evading his responsibilities.
At her cousin's wedding, Sitara wrongly assumes Salar is the photographer. Salar develops a soft spot for Sitara after seeing how poorly she is treated. However, due to a conspiracy, objections arise about their closeness. Salar, once again, avoids the issue, leaving Sitara to face doubts from her own family.
Can Sitara prove she’s not guilty? Will Salar help her avoid further mistreatment? Will her family support Sitara? Can Salar show he genuinely cares? Will there be more plots against Sitara?

snippet.title: Rakesh Barot | Hathe Meli Lal Mehandi | Reshma Thakor | હાથે મેલી લાલ મહેંદી | Gujarati New Song
snippet.description:
Jhankar Music Gujarati Presents Latest Video Song titled "Hathe Meli Lal Mehandi" .હાથે મેલી લાલ મહેંદી  Sung by Rakesh Barot, Reshma, Thakor Penned by Manu Rabari, Maulik Desai, & Music Composed by Rakesh Barot, Mehul Barot & Starring : Rakesh Barot, Sweta Sen, Veena Tank & Directed by Bhavesh Gorasiya  
Join this channel to get access to perks:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCQeljbfXMX_5a2_KMXTkF-A/join  
-----------------------------
🎧 𝐀𝐮𝐝𝐢𝐨 𝐂𝐫𝐞𝐝𝐢𝐭𝐬 : 
♪ Song :  Hathe Meli Lal Mehandi
♪ Singer : Rakesh Barot, Reshma Thakor
♪ Lyrics :  Manu Rabari,Maulik Desai
♪ Music :  Rakesh Barot, Mehul Barot
♪ Studio : Dhoon Digital Recording Studio, Adalaj

#rakeshbarot #kanuda_bhajan #jhankarmusicgujarati #krishnasong #krishna #krishnastatus 

🎬 𝐅𝐮𝐥𝐥 𝐕𝐢𝐝𝐞𝐨 𝐂𝐫𝐞𝐝𝐢𝐭𝐬 : 
♪ Producer: MAARSS MOVIES AND MUSIC (JHANKAR MUSIC)
♪ Executive Producer: Red Velvet Cinema 
♪ Project Lead By : Chandu Raval
♪ Starring  : Rakesh Barot,Sweta Sen , Veena Tank
♪ D.O.P and Editing : Anu Patel ( Viral )
♪ Director: Bhavesh Gorasiya
♪ Concept : Savya Bhati , Bhavesh Gorsiya
♪ Creative Producer: Dhyey Films & Team
♪ Technical support: Jenish Talaviya 
♪ Production: Pushpa Shah
♪ Light: Kalpesh Jadav 
♪ Choreographer: Deepak Turi 
♪ Makeup-Hair: Hasmukh Limbachiya 
♪ Rakesh Barot Costume: Manisha R Barot, Vishva Selection
♪ Spot: Raju N Akshay, Guna Kaka 
♪ Poster: Raj Charoliya
♪ Location : Swapna Shrushti
♪ Music Label: Jhankar Music

-----------------------------
📝 𝐋𝐲𝐫𝐢𝐜𝐬: Gujarati  👇

𝐌: હે હાથે મેલી લાલ મહેંદીયો પરવાર્યા શો ચો
     હે તમે હાથે મેલી લાલ મહેંદીયો પરવાર્યા શો ચો
     હે ફરો અલગ તમે મુડ માં અમને કોક તો કો
𝐅: હે ટોનટ ના મારો શાંતિ તમે રાખો
     પરવાર તો ચો હજી કરીયો મેં આખો 
𝐌: કાજળ ભરેલી તારી કાળી કાળી આંખો
      સૂરજ ને પણ એ કરી નાખે જોખો
𝐅: હે બાર મહિના થી કરુ ધહાણી પેર્યુ ઓઢિયુ કોઈ ચો
𝐌: હે પેરો તમે પેરો, પેરો ઓઢો ને પરવારો ના ચો કઉ શુ કયા...

𝐅: હો તૈયાર થઈ ને તમે ફરો બાર મહિના
     અમે આજ પરવારા તો ડોળા ઘાઢો કઈના 
𝐌: જા જા જુઠી હોંભળયા હમાચર બુન ને જમાઈ ના
      એટલે નાહિ જાવુ તારે ઘરે તારા ભાઈ ના
𝐅: હો પોર આઠમ ના ટોણે આવુજ કરીયુ તુ 
     દાબ બતાવી મારજો અમે માડી વાલ્યુ તુ
𝐌: હે હગા વાલા કે વહુ બહુ હારી
      તે મારા બાની સેવા ઘણી કરી 
𝐅: હે તમારા ને મારા માવતર જુદા ગણ્યા સે મે ચો
𝐌: એટલે તો કહુ છુ મારી વાલી ઘડીએ દૂર ના થો...

𝐅: હો ફોન કરી ને બુન ને તેડાયા સે અમે
    ટોનટ મારવા ના ખોટા રેવાદો ને તમે
𝐌: હે વાલી મારી હાચે હાચુ કહીદુ હમ ખઈ ને માના
      તારા વગર ચાલતુ નથી એટલે કરું બાના
𝐅: હો એટલે તો કઉ છુ શાંતિ તમે રાખો
     તમને પડવા નહિ દુ કોઈ વખો
𝐌: હે યાદ આવે આ તારા વાલાપ ની વાતો
      દાડો તો જાય પણ જાતી નથી રાતો
𝐅: હે વાલા આજે સાતમ તો હેડી કાલ નો દાડો રયો
𝐌: હે એક દાડો યુગ જેવડો કાઢવો મારે ચો
𝐅: હે હેડો મારી હંગાથ માં હાહરે કોક દાડો રો
𝐌: હે હુ તો મજાક, મજાક કરું મારી માનતી જઈ આવો તમે જો
      વળજો વેલા હર... 

📝 𝐋𝐲𝐫𝐢𝐜𝐬: English  👇

𝐌: He Hathe Meli Lal Mehandiyo Parvaya Sho Cho
   He Tame Hathe Meli Lal Mehandiyo Parvaya Sho Cho
   He Faro Tame Alag Mud Ma Amane Kok To Ko
𝐅: He Tonat Na Maro Shanti Tame Rakho
    Parvar To Haji Karyo Chaya Me Aakho
𝐌: Kajal Bhareli Tari Kali Kali Aankho
     Suraj Ne Pan Ae Kari Nakhe Jokho
𝐅: He Bar Mahina Thi Karu Gharni Peryu Odhiyu Koi Cho
𝐌: He Prero Tame Per, Pero Odho Ne Parvaro Na Cho Kau Shu Kaya

𝐅: Ho Taiyar Thai Ne Tame Faro Bar Mahina
    Ame Aaje Parvara To Dola Ghadho Kaina 
𝐌: Ja Ja Tuthi Hombhala Hamachar Bun Ne Jamani Na
     Aetale Nahi Javu Tare Ghare Tara Bhai Na
𝐅: Ho Por Aatham Na Dade Aavuj Karyu Tu 
    Dab Manjo Ame Madi Valyu Tu
𝐌: He Haga Vala Ke Vahu Bahu Hari
     Te Mara Bani Seva Ghani Kari 
𝐅: He Tamara Ne Amara Mavtar Juda Ganya Se Me Cho
𝐌: Aetle To Kahu Chhu Mari Vali Ghadiae Dur Na Tho

𝐅: Ho Phone Kari Ne Bun Ne Tedaya Se Amese
    Tonat Marava Na Khota Revado Ne Tame
𝐌: He Vali Mari Hache Hachu Kahidu Ham Khai Ne Mana
     Tara Vagar Chaltu Nathi Aetle Karu Bana
𝐅: Ho Aetle kau Chhu Shanti Tame Rakho
    Tamne Padva Nahi Du Koi Vakho
𝐌: He Yad Aave Se Tara Valap Ni Aa Vato
     Dado To Jay Pan Jati Nathi Rato
𝐅: He Vala Aaje To Satam Hedi Kal No Dado Rayo
𝐌: He Ek Dado Yug Jevado Kadhavo Mare Cho
𝐅: He Hedo Mari Hangath Ma Hahare Kok Dado Ro
𝐌: He Huto Majak, Majak Karu Mari Maniti Jai Aavo Tame Jo
     Valjo Vela Har
---------------------------------
@𝐄𝐱𝐜𝐥𝐮𝐬𝐢𝐯𝐞𝐥𝐲 𝐨𝐧 𝐉𝐡𝐚𝐧𝐤𝐚𝐫 𝐌𝐮𝐬𝐢𝐜 𝐆𝐮𝐣𝐚𝐫𝐚𝐭𝐢

     હે તમે હાથે મેલી લાલ મહેંદીયો પરવાર્યા શો ચો

snippet.description: Today we made a spicy Buffalo pickle in our Village . First we brought a whole buffalo . We made it into small pieces after a proper cleaning. You can check it out here for the village style recipes .

snippet.title: World’s Deadliest Battle | The Mahabharat Series | Ep 1 | Vikram Aditya  | Telugu
snippet.description:
Welcome to the first episode in our series on the Mahabharat, one of the greatest epics ever written. In this drama, we delve into the profound truth that there are no purely good or bad people, only good and bad circumstances.
In this episode, we explore Vyasa's visionary experience that led to the creation of this timeless epic. Discover how Vyasa, after dividing the Vedas, received a haunting vision of a catastrophic war—The Mahabharat. Disturbed and eager to document every detail, Vyasa chose the only being capable of keeping up with his narration, Lord Ganesha, to write down the untold story of his descendants.
Our storytelling is not just about revisiting ancient tales; it's about extracting timeless wisdom to confront modern challenges. This episode lays the foundation for understanding the Mahabharat's depth, where virtue and vice intertwine, revealing critical life lessons.
